The '''New Republic Archaeological Corps''' was an organization of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] hastily formed with the rediscovery of [[Ossus/Legends|Ossus]]. They were one of the leading research agencies involved in excavations on that [[Planet/Legends|planet]]. During the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]], they [[Mission to Ossus|investigated]] rumors that [[Yuuzhan Vong]] were exploring the Ossus ruins for secrets they could exploit in their attempted extermination of the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]].

